#: src/ui/preferences.ui:20
msgid ""
"The code word count determines the security of the transfer.\n"
"\n"
"A short code is easy to remember but increases the risk of someone else guessing the code. As a code may only be guessed once, the risk is very small even with short codes. A length of 4 is very secure."
msgstr ""
"Koddagi soʻzlar soni uzatishning xavfsizligini belgilaydi.\n"
"\n"
"Qisqa kodni eslab qolish oson, lekin bu kodni boshqa birov topib olish xavfini oshiradi. Kodni faqat bir marta taxmin qilish mumkinligi sababli, hatto qisqa kodlar bilan ham xavf juda kichik. 4 ga teng uzunlik juda xavfsiz."

#: src/ui/preferences.ui:25
msgid "Code Word Count"
msgstr "Koddagi soʻzlar soni"

