#: src/ui/welcome_dialog.ui:97
msgid ""
"Warp makes file transfer simple. To get started, both parties need to install Warp on their devices.\n"
"\n"
"After selecting a file to transmit, the sender needs to tell the receiver the displayed transmit code. This is preferably done via a secure communication channel.\n"
"\n"
"When the receiver has entered the code, the file transfer can begin.\n"
"\n"
"For more information about Warp, open the Help section from the Main Menu."
msgstr ""
"Warp fayllarni uzatishni osonlashtiradi. Ishni boshlash uchun ikkala tomon ham oʻz qurilmalariga Warp ilovasini oʻrnatishi kerak.\n"
"\n"
"Uzatish uchun fayl tanlangandan soʻng, joʻnatuvchi qabul qiluvchiga koʻrsatilgan uzatish kodini aytishi kerak. Buni himoyalangan aloqa kanali orqali amalga oshirgan ma’qul.\n"
"\n"
"Qabul qiluvchi kodni kiritgach, fayl uzatishni boshlash mumkin.\n"
"\n"
"Warp haqida koʻproq ma’lumot olish uchun Asosiy menyudan Yordam boʻlimini oching."

